 employment platform that grows with your business, from contractor management to full entity setup. EOR with two options: Fixed Rate (Zero FX) at $599 / £479 per emp / month, flat with no FX line, or Regional Rate at £400 + 2% FX shown explicitly, cross-border only. Named specialists in 180+ countries."/><meta name="application-name" content="Teamed"/><link rel="author" href="https://www.teamed.global"/><meta name="author" content="Teamed"/><meta name="creator" content="Teamed"/><meta name="publisher" content="Teamed Ltd"/><meta name="robots" content="index, follow"/><meta name="googlebot" content="index, follow, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1"/><link rel="canonical" href="https://www.teamed.global"/><meta property="og:title" content="teamed. — Global Employment Management and Operations"/><meta property="og:description" content="GEMO — the only employment platform that grows with your business. Contractor → EOR → entity, on one system. FX margin disclosed where it applies — 0% on the Fixed Rate, 2% explicit on the Regional Rate (cross-border only)."/><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.teamed.global"/><meta property="og:site_name" content="Teamed"/><meta property="og:locale" content="en_GB"/><meta property="og:image" content="https://www.teamed.global/og/teamed-og-default.webp"/><meta property="og:image:width" content="1200"/><meta property="og:image:height" content="630"/><meta property="og:image:alt" content="Airmail postcard from teamed. — &quot;Wishing you only the best.&quot; To: the founder looking for a partner they can trust."/><meta property="og:type" content="website"/><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"/><meta name="twitter:title" content="teamed. — Global Employment Management and Operations"/><meta name="twitter:description" content="GEMO — contractor → EOR → entity, one system. FX margin disclosed line-by-line (0% Fixed Rate / 2% Regional Rate, cross-border only). Named specialists in 180+ countries."/><meta name