inkedin.com/in/antonyvallee/"],"description":"Antony Vallee is the co-founder and CEO of Teamed. A serial entrepreneur, he started the firm after seeing first-hand how time-consuming and isolating cross-border hiring had become for both employers and remote employees. He sets Teamed's commercial direction and works alongside Head of Legal Joanna Castens and co-founder Tom Price-Daniel on the firm's named-specialist EOR model."},{"@type":"Person","name":"Tom Price-Daniel","sameAs":["https://www.linkedin.com/in/tompricedaniel/"],"description":"Tom Price-Daniel is a co-founder of Teamed and the firm's jurisdiction specialist, based in Madrid. He works across multi-jurisdiction payroll, Indian tax residency, and APAC compliance, and authors Teamed's editorial on EOR-vs-entity decisions and global employment platform comparisons. He spotted the 2026 India tax-residency shift two months before the platform alerts, onboarding five clients around it without dispute."}],"industry":"Other B2B SaaS"}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebSite","url":"https://www.teamed.global","name":"Teamed","description":"From first contractor to full entity — the whole planet, one platform.","publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Teamed Ltd"}}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":"SiteNavigationElement","@id":"https://www.teamed.global/#nav/about","name":"About","url":"https://www.teamed.global/about","position":1},{"@type":"SiteNavigationElement","@id":"https://www.teamed.global/#nav/for-hr-managers","name":"For HR Teams","url":"https://www.teamed.global/for-hr-managers","position":2,"isPartOf":{"@id":"https://www.teamed.global/#nav#"}},{"@type":"SiteNavigationElement","@id":"https://www.teamed.global/#nav/for-legal-teams","name":"For Legal Teams","url":"https://www.teamed.global/for-legal-teams","position":3,"isPartOf":{"@id":"https://www.teamed.global/#nav#"}},{"@type":"SiteNa