ur, he started the firm after seeing first-hand how time-consuming and isolating cross-border hiring had become for both employers and remote employees. He sets Teamed's commercial direction and works alongside Head of Legal Joanna Castens and co-founder Tom Price-Daniel on the firm's named-specialist EOR model.\"},{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Tom Price-Daniel\",\"sameAs\":[\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tompricedaniel/\"],\"description\":\"Tom Price-Daniel is a co-founder of Teamed and the firm's jurisdiction specialist, based in Madrid. He works across multi-jurisdiction payroll, Indian tax residency, and APAC compliance, and authors Teamed's editorial on EOR-vs-entity decisions and global employment platform comparisons. He spotted the 2026 India tax-residency shift two months before the platform alerts, onboarding five clients around it without dispute.\"}],\"industry\":\"Other B2B SaaS\"}"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"12:T1733,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"SiteNavigationElement\",\"@id\":\"https://www.teamed.global/#nav/about\",\"name\":\"About\",\"url\":\"https://www.teamed.global/about\",\"position\":1},{\"@type\":\"SiteNavigationElement\",\"@id\":\"https://www.teamed.global/#nav/for-hr-managers\",\"name\":\"For HR Teams\",\"url\":\"https://www.teamed.global/for-hr-managers\",\"position\":2,\"isPartOf\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.teamed.global/#nav#\"}},{\"@type\":\"SiteNavigationElement\",\"@id\":\"https://www.teamed.global/#nav/for-legal-teams\",\"name\":\"For Legal Teams\",\"url\":\"https://www.teamed.global/for-legal-teams\",\"position\":3,\"isPartOf\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.teamed.global/#nav#\"}},{\"@type\":\"SiteNavigationElement\",\"@id\":\"https://www.teamed.global/#nav/for-finance-managers\",\"name\":\"For Finance Teams\",\"url\":\"https://www.teamed.global/for-finance-managers\",\"position\":4,\"isPartOf\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.teamed.global/#nav#\"}},{\"@type\":